    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还记得小时候吗？那时的街道就是你的领地，每一个路沿、水坑或人行道都能变为一场场史诗级的任务。<strong>Bambas!</strong> 将带你重温那种魔力。这款沙盒游戏凭借其创新的操控系统，让你再次沉浸于那些街头冒险的乐趣之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274390/extras/fee7de0d1ba07170189fb12a82967a2c.poster.avif?t=1768493978\" width=632 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274390/extras/fee7de0d1ba07170189fb12a82967a2c.webm?t=1768493978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274390/extras/fee7de0d1ba07170189fb12a82967a2c.mp4?t=1768493978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个充满活力和细节的地中海海滨城市，在这里，创意是唯一的规则，而探索就是你通往快乐的护照。你可以通过手柄的摇杆和扳机分别控制每只鞋，就像在操控自己的双脚。简单地向前走可不够，你得跨过斑马线、踢开易拉罐、在路沿上保持平衡，甚至完成令人惊叹的跳跃，来克服数百个挑战并解锁无数可定制的运动鞋款式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274390/extras/fbc20570332c946e5261de5a6bed28d0.poster.avif?t=1768493978\" width=718 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274390/extras/fbc20570332c946e5261de5a6bed28d0.webm?t=1768493978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274390/extras/fbc20570332c946e5261de5a6bed28d0.mp4?t=1768493978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Bambas!</strong> 不仅仅是一款游戏，它更是对城市文化的致敬。通过非线性的叙事和沉浸式的故事表达，它打破了各种刻板印象。在转角处发现新故事，在隐藏的角落中发掘秘密，与那些引领你走向未知的角色相遇。穿上你的 Bambas，走上街头，因为在这款游戏中，每一步都承载着独特的个性与风格，开启一场场精彩的冒险！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274390/extras/2ed1e3023550391379a11112dbc02e12.avif?t=1768493978\" width=614 height=72 /></span></p>",
